For the server I opted for Ubuntu server 22.04 and for the workstation I opted for Ubuntu desktop on PC under virtualisation via Virtualbox.


![Screenshot 2026-01-11 190745.png](./images/Screenshot 2026-01-11 190745.png)

The system architecture incoporates a dual-machine design. 
The Ubuntu server runs with no graphical interface A VirtualBox Host-Only network ensures traffic remains isolated from external networks, supporting ethical and secure testing. A firewall restricts SSH access so only the workstation can connect.
